OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FThe Foreign Office has confirmed it is
OL,8,Fsupporting the family of a British man
OL,9,Fin Dubai after Katie Price revealed
OL,10,Fher husband, Lee Andrews, is "missing".
OL,12,FThe former glamour model and reality
OL,13,FTV star said in a podcast on Saturday
OL,14,Fthat she had not heard from Mr
OL,15,FAndrews, who lives in the UAE, for
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
