OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FWhen asked by ITV News about the
OL,8,Fcomments on Monday, a Foreign Office
OL,9,Fspokesperson said: "We are supporting
OL,10,Fthe family of a British man and are in
OL,11,Fcontact with the local authorities."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FPrice shared a video on her social
OL,19,Fmedia, saying she thought her husband
OL,20,Fmay have been kidnapped or arrested,
OL,21,Fwith a plea to help find him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
