OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FShe said: "The truth is, Lee has been
OL,8,Fmissing for three days. Lee was trying
OL,9,Fto get through the border near Hatta
OL,10,Fand, oh God, this is so
OL,11,Fdiscombobulating.
OL,13,F"His location went off at 10.03pm
OL,14,FWednesday night, that's the last
OL,15,Fcontact anyone's had, his family and
OL,16,Fme. This is the third day now... He
OL,17,Fphoned me before the location went
OL,18,Foff. He's in the middle of nowhere.
OL,19,FObviously, I'm worried."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
