OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FShe added: "The last FaceTime call I
OL,8,Fhad with him... he had ties around his
OL,9,Fhand and a hood. He sounded really
OL,10,Fworried and said like whispering,
OL,11,F'They're coming for me now. They're
OL,12,Fcoming for me. I've got to go.'"
OL,14,FKatie Price shared this video on her
OL,15,FYouTube account on Saturday,
OL,16,Fexplaining that she was in contact
OL,17,Fwith Dubai Police after not speaking
OL,18,Fwith her husband Lee Andrews for three
OL,19,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
