OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FThe saga began after the 43-year-old
OL,8,FDubai-based businessman failed to show
OL,9,Fup for their joint appearance on ITV's
OL,10,FGood Morning Britain last Tuesday,
OL,11,Fclaiming he had "things to do" but was
OL,12,Fon his way.
OL,14,FHowever, according to Price, producers
OL,15,Fof the ITV programme had spoken to the
OL,16,FForeign Office who said they had
OL,17,Fdetained a British man with Lee's name
OL,18,Fand date of birth.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
