OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FWhen asked if Andrews had been
OL,8,Farrested at the airport, Price said:
OL,9,F"I just said, 'Lee, apparently a
OL,10,FBritish man has been detained. Can you
OL,11,Fjust confirm that it's not you?'
OL,12,FBecause I obviously know it's not him.
OL,14,F"So, he's just done a voice note back
OL,15,Fand laughing emojis. 'No, it's not me'
OL,16,Fand a voice note. And he's just sent
OL,17,Fme pictures."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
