OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FSpeaking on her podcast The Katie
OL,8,FPrice Show last Thursday, Katie
OL,9,Faddressed comments she'd received that
OL,10,FAndrews was a conman.
OL,12,FPrice explained that during their four-
OL,13,Fmonth marriage Andrews has not visited
OL,14,Fher in the UK, despite repeatedly
OL,15,Fsaying that he would on social media.
OL,17,FThis led to her followers questioning
OL,18,Fif there was a reason he couldn't fly
OL,19,Fto the UK, including the suggestion he
OL,20,Fwas on a no-fly list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
