OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FPrice said she understood fans'
OL,8,Fconcerns, saying: "If you can't fly
OL,9,Fout of Dubai for whatever reason just
OL,10,Ftell me... If he doesn't come to
OL,11,FEngland, I've said I want answers. A
OL,12,Fbit of respect. Just tell me what's
OL,13,Fgoing on."
OL,15,FShe added: "You either tell me what's
OL,16,Fgoing on, or what does he expect to do
OL,17,Fbecause I'm not flying out to Dubai
OL,18,Fnow. I've got family here, I've got my
OL,19,Fkids here, I've got work to do."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
