OL,3,CKatie Price's 'missing' husband:
OL,4,CForeign Office 'supporting family'
OL,5,Camid claims
OL,7,FKatie and Lee married in January, just
OL,8,Fdays after they met in person in Dubai.
OL,10,FIt is Price's fourth marriage. She
OL,11,Ffirst wed Australian singer Peter
OL,12,FAndre in 2005, eventually getting
OL,13,Fdivorced in 2009. She then married
OL,14,Fcage fighter Alex Reid between 2010
OL,15,Fand 2012.
OL,17,FHer longest marriage was to Kieran
OL,18,FHayler, from 2013 until 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
